;Below is the NPC data for the various maps on this bank. Each NPC has 4 bytes of data stored here.
;The first byte is the index to their tile patterns. If the MSB is set on the first byte, the NPC
;will be stationary. If the MSB is clear, the NPC will walk around while off screen. The second
;byte is the dialog index. The third, byte is their X position on the map. The fourth byte is their
;Y position on the map. Below are the GFX indexes and which NPCs they represent:
